Is the home of the Darling family.
彼得潘之所以選中了這棟房子

24
00:02:14,377 --> 00:02:16,588
And Peter Pan chose this particular house...
是因為這裡住的人中

25
00:02:17,005 --> 00:02:19,716
Because there were people here who believed in him.
有人相信他的存在

26
00:02:20,425 --> 00:02:22,052
