29
00:02:28,433 --> 00:02:30,185
Mrs. Darling believed that Peter Pan...
達林太太相信彼得潘

30
00:02:30,810 --> 00:02:33,813
Was the spirit of youth, but Mr. Darling
是屬於小時候的精靈,但是達林先生呢…

31
00:02:34,272 --> 00:02:37,150
mary, unless I find my cuff links,
瑪莉，除非你找到我的袖扣

32
00:02:37,317 --> 00:02:38,527
we don't go to the party.
否則我們就不去

33
00:02:39,194 --> 00:02:40,445
And if we don't go to the party.
但假如我們不參加的話

34
00:02:40,737 --> 00:02:42,531
