我就永遠不用再到公司去了

35
00:02:43,323 --> 00:02:44,574
And if I... Ouch!
假如我永遠不…哦!

36
00:02:45,242 --> 00:02:48,203
Well, Mr. Darling was a practical man.
當然啦 達林先生是一個特殊人物

37
00:02:49,371 --> 00:02:51,915
The boys, however, John and Michael,
無論如何 約翰和麥克都相信

38
00:02:52,833 --> 00:02:54,793
believed Peter Pan was a real person,
彼得潘是真實的人

39
00:02:55,544 --> 00:02:58,296
and made him the hero of all their nursery games.
而且是他們遊戲中的英雄

40
00:02:58,922 --> 00:03:00,549
Blast you, Peter Pan.
去死吧，彼得潘

41
00:03:04,261 --> 00:03:05,762
Give up, Captain Hook?
虎克船長，投降吧 休想!

42
00:03:05,929 --> 00:03:09,474
Give up? I'll teach you to cut off me hand!
我來教你怎麼樣 砍掉我的右手

43
00:03:09,933 --> 00:03:11,142
Oh, no, John.
約翰，不對

44
00:03:11,434 --> 00:03:12,561
It was the left hand.
