45
00:03:13,478 --> 00:03:14,938
Oh, yes. Thankyou, Wendy.
噢，對了 謝謝你啊，溫蒂

46
00:03:15,564 --> 00:03:18,525
Wendy, the eldest, not only believed,
溫蒂，最大的孩子

47
00:03:19,693 --> 00:03:21,736
