她的確盡忠職守守

53
00:03:34,207 --> 00:03:37,586
and viewed the whole affair with a certain tolerance.
而且很能容忍所有的事情

54
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,510
Take that!
打死你…

55
00:03:46,928 --> 00:03:48,847
